                <div class="rendering rendering_researchoutput  rendering_researchoutput_standard rendering_contributiontojournal rendering_standard rendering_contributiontojournal_standard"><a rel="ContributionToJournal" href="https://research.rug.nl/en/publications/psychotropic-drug-prescribing-before-and-during-the-covid-19-pand/" class="link"><span><strong>Psychotropic drug prescribing before and during the COVID-19 pandemic among people with depressive and anxiety disorders: A multinational network study.</strong></span></a> / Luo, Hao; Chai, Yi; Li, Sijia et al. <br />In: <a rel="Journal" href="#" class="link"><span>The Lancet Psychiatry</span></a>, Vol. 11, No. 10, 10.2024, p. 807-817.<p class="type"><span class="type_family">Research output<span class="type_family_sep">: </span></span><span class="type_classification_parent">Contribution to journal<span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span></span><span class="type_classification">Article</span><span class="type_classification"><span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span>Academic</span><span class="type_classification"><span class="type_parent_sep"> › </span>peer-review</span></p></div>
